Comment: 0,0:23:54.25,0:23:58.08,END,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H72ABF0&\blur3\bord3}彷彿讓我更加堅強
Comment: 0,0:23:58.08,0:24:02.00,END,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H72ABF0&\blur3\bord3}就算錯覺也不要緊
Comment: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:07.68,END,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H72ABF0&\blur3\bord3}全速穿過彎道吧
Comment: 0,0:24:07.68,0:24:11.30,END,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H72ABF0&\blur3\bord3}拍一拍手 身體動起來
Comment: 0,0:24:11.30,0:24:15.98,END,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H72ABF0&\blur3\bord3}這份心情難以描述
Comment: 0,0:24:15.98,0:24:22.73,END,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H72ABF0&\blur3\bord3}但依然要自由地表達出來
Comment: 0,0:24:22.73,0:24:27.40,END,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H72ABF0&\blur3\bord3}過山車上沐浴著一瞬的光輝
Comment: 0,0:24:27.40,0:24:30.61,END,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H72ABF0&\blur3\bord3}一同前往彩虹的另一端
Comment: 0,0:24:30.61,0:24:35.16,END,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H72ABF0&\blur3\bord3}時而爬升 有稍微下降
Comment: 0,0:24:35.16,0:24:39.71,END,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H72ABF0&\blur3\bord3}上下顛倒也要歡笑不斷
Comment: 0,0:24:39.71,0:24:43.63,END,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H72ABF0&\blur3\bord3}只要有你 我們一起
Comment: 0,0:24:43.63,0:24:46.46,END,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H72ABF0&\blur3\bord3}就什麼也不怕！
Comment: 0,0:24:49.76,0:24:50.63,END,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H72ABF0&\blur3\bord3}Let's dream!
